Package: ShinyRenamingNDIDI
Type: Package
Title: Image Renaming Tool for Nutrient Deficiency Research
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("User", "Name", email = "user@example.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: A Shiny application for standardized renaming and compression of 
    nutrient deficiency images. Allows researchers to upload images, select 
    metadata (crop, nutrient deficiency, phenological stage, deficiency stage),
    and download renamed and compressed images in a ZIP file.
